<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 18:17:14 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>人工智能订单抵消了中国销售额下降后，ASMI 上调了季度指引</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asmi-raises-quarterly-guidance-after-ai-orders-offset-chinese-sales-drop-2024-07-23/</link><description>计算机芯片制造设备供应商 ASM 国际公司 (ASMI) 周二表示，由于人工智能相关产品抵消了中国销售额的下降，第二季度订单超出预期，该公司上调了第三季度指引。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 17:08:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/asmi-raises-quarterly-guidance-after-ai-orders-offset-chinese-sales-drop-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>渔业条约在世贸组织失败引发中美担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/fishing-treaty-fails-wto-prompting-us-chinese-concern-2024-07-23/</link><description>周二，削减渔业补贴的条约草案未能通过后，各国和环保组织表达了担忧和失望，中国呼吁各国对世界贸易组织的谈判方式进行重大改变。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 16:54:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/fishing-treaty-fails-wto-prompting-us-chinese-concern-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>据《Information》报道，苹果最早可能会在 2026 年发布可折叠 iPhone</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-likely-release-foldable-iphone-early-2026-information-reports-2024-07-23/</link><description>据周二报道，苹果公司可能最早在 2026 年推出可折叠 iPhone，这可能标志着该公司最受欢迎产品的最大硬件设计改造。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 16:53:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-likely-release-foldable-iphone-early-2026-information-reports-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>奢侈品消费放缓导致 LVMH 销售额未达预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/lvmh-sales-grow-1-second-quarter-2024-07-23/</link><description>路威酩轩第二季度销售额放缓，原因是消费者因价格上涨而不愿在高端时装上大肆挥霍，这可能无法让担心奢侈品行业增长放缓的投资者感到安心。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 15:59:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/lvmh-sales-grow-1-second-quarter-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>联合国驻也门特使表示，胡塞武装对红海航运的威胁正在加剧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/houthi-threat-red-sea-shipping-is-growing-says-un-envoy-yemen-2024-07-23/</link><description>联合国驻也门特使汉斯·格伦德伯格周二向联合国安理会表示，红海及周边水道的最新事态发展表明，也门胡塞武装对国际航运的威胁正在加剧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 15:17:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/middle-east/houthi-threat-red-sea-shipping-is-growing-says-un-envoy-yemen-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰外长抵达中国讨论“公平和平”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/ukraines-foreign-minister-arrives-china-discuss-fair-peace-2024-07-23/</link><description>乌克兰外长周二抵达中国，与外交部长王毅举行会谈，讨论如何在与俄罗斯的战争中实现“公平和平”，并讨论双边关系。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 14:27:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/ukraines-foreign-minister-arrives-china-discuss-fair-peace-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>中国在兴奋剂纠纷中向美国挑战金牌炫耀权</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/china-challenge-us-gold-medal-bragging-rights-amid-doping-rout-2024-07-23/</link><description>中国来到巴黎奥运会，期待着近几十年来亚洲体育强国屡见不鲜的金牌潮，但兴奋剂纠纷的阴影却笼罩着代表团。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 13:20:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/olympics/china-challenge-us-gold-medal-bragging-rights-amid-doping-rout-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>印度财政部长支持增加中国直接投资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/indias-finance-minister-backs-increasing-chinese-direct-investment-2024-07-23/</link><description>自2020年以来，新德里与北京关系日益紧张，导致资金流动受到干扰，印度财政部长支持其经济顾问的建议，允许更多中国投资进入该国。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 12:20:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/indias-finance-minister-backs-increasing-chinese-direct-investment-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，中国电动卡车初创公司 Windrose 将在美国 IPO 前筹集 2 亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-electric-truck-startup-windrose-raise-200-mln-before-us-ipo-source-says-2024-07-23/</link><description>一位直接知情人士透露，中国电动卡车初创公司 Windrose 计划在最后一轮股权投资和债务融资中筹集 2 亿美元，然后再寻求在美国进行首次公开​​募股。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 11:17:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-electric-truck-startup-windrose-raise-200-mln-before-us-ipo-source-says-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>厄瓜多尔海军准备打击加拉帕戈斯群岛周围的非法捕鱼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/ecuadors-navy-ready-combat-illegal-fishing-around-galapagos-islands-2024-07-23/</link><description>厄瓜多尔海军在与邻国盟友进行训练演习后，准备保护加拉帕戈斯群岛周围海域免受外国船只的非法捕鱼，这些船只每年都会到访，威胁该群岛水域的海洋野生动物。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 11:01:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/ecuadors-navy-ready-combat-illegal-fishing-around-galapagos-islands-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>通用汽车超出季度预期并上调预测，但股价跳水</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/gm-beats-second-quarter-expectations-raises-forecast-again-2024-07-23/</link><description>通用汽车周二公布的第二季度利润和收入超出了华尔街的预期，并在强劲的定价和汽油动力卡车需求的推动下，今年第二次上调了年度利润预期。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 10:31:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/gm-beats-second-quarter-expectations-raises-forecast-again-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：巨型股报告，哈里斯在框架内，中国摇摆不定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-07-23/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 10:17:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>五角大楼表达担忧后，克里姆林宫表示俄罗斯与中国的北极合作不针对任何人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/kremlin-says-russian-arctic-cooperation-with-china-is-not-aimed-against-anyone-2024-07-23/</link><description>克里姆林宫周二表示，俄罗斯与中国在北极的合作并不针对任何其他国家，并表示美国对此类工作的批评是错误的。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 09:53:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/kremlin-says-russian-arctic-cooperation-with-china-is-not-aimed-against-anyone-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>Forvia 和比亚迪将亚洲合作伙伴关系带到欧洲</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/forvia-byd-bring-asian-partnership-europe-2024-07-23/</link><description>全球第七大汽车零部件供应商 Forvia 周二表示，将把与中国电池专家和汽车制造商比亚迪的合作伙伴关系带到欧洲。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 09:16:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/forvia-byd-bring-asian-partnership-europe-2024-07-23/</guid></item><item><title>印度削减智能手机进口税以提振苹果</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-budget-india-cuts-import-tax-smartphones-boost-apple-2024-07-23/</link><description>印度宣布将手机和部分关键零部件的进口关税从20%下调至15%，此举将直接让苹果公司受益，尽管苹果公司在当地产量增加，但仍向印度进口高端智能手机。</description><pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 08:42:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-budget-india-cuts-import-tax-smartphones-boost-apple-2024-07-23/</guid></item></channel></rss>